snippet.title: Arknights Official Concept Trailer 1
snippet.description:
English version of Arknights is coming winter 2019. Stay tuned to participate in Arknights community events on our social media channels:

Official Discord Server:
https://discordapp.com/invite/arknights

Official Twitter Account:
https://twitter.com/ArknightsEN

Official Facebook Page:
https://www.facebook.com/ArknightsGlobal/

Official Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/arknights_messenger_official/

Arknights is a strategic RPG mobile game with a fantasy theme.

【Monster】
Original Composer: Johnny Lee Andrews* / Dustin Bates* / Rob Graves
OP: Johnny Lee Andrews Music (Big Deal) /Razor and Tie Music Publishing & True Anomaly Music (Concord Music)
SP : Peermusic (S.E. Asia) Ltd.

#Arknights #Yostar #Starset
